oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Performance - Tommy Cash - 2016-05-20
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Performance by Tommy Cash from the Ford Theater at the Country Music Hall of Fame and Museum on May 20, 2016. Part of the Cash on Cash series?? Appearance made for Cosmos tours.

oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dcterms:tableOfContents: Performance includes; Big River (begins abruptly in progress) -- Folsom Prison Blues -- I Guess Things Happen That Way -- Hey Porter/Cry, Cry, Cry -- Bandy, The Rodeo Clown (Clayton Claxton) -- I Still Miss Someone -- Daddy Sang Bass -- Rise And Shine -- Six White Horses -- Medley (I Walk The Line / A Boy Named Sue / One Piece At A Time / I Got Stripes / Folsom Prison Blues -- Cannonball Rag (Dave Daeger) -- The Greatest Voice Is Gone -- The Way That We're Living -- Today I Started Loving You Again (Clayton Claxton) -- That's Alright, Mama -- Sunday Morning Coming Down.
